'''世界盃女子棒球賽'''（Women's Baseball World Cup）是由[[世界棒壘球聯盟|世界棒壘球聯盟]]主辦的國際性[[女子棒球|女子棒球]]賽事。首屆賽事於2004年在[[加拿大|加拿大]]舉行，每兩年舉辦一次，2012年獲得[[國際棒球總會|國際棒球總會]]承認。目前本賽事採七局制。
其地位與男子的[[世界棒球經典賽|世界棒球經典賽]]相呼應。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wbsc.org/tournaments/2016-womens-baseball-world-cup/news/wbsc-awards-florida-based-usssa-hosting-rights-for-womens-baseball-world-cup-2018/ |title=WBSC awards Florida-based USSSA hosting rights for Women’s Baseball World Cup 2018 |last1= |first1= |date=October 12, 2017 |website=World Baseball Softball Confederation |publisher= |access-date=January 5, 2018 |archive-date=2017-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223160616/http://www.wbsc.org/tournaments/2016-womens-baseball-world-cup/news/wbsc-awards-florida-based-usssa-hosting-rights-for-womens-baseball-world-cup-2018/ }}</ref>

